description:
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;An exciting opportunity to support the Children&#39;s Hospital during the COVID pandemic.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;Do you have the skills and experience to make a difference to Children requiring admission to Leicester&#39;s Children&#39;s Hospital this winter? &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;We are able to support our Children&#39;s hospital this winter by offering a range of Band 5 positions across Children’s Surgical Wards at the Leicester Royal Infirmary in Leicester.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;The children we care for are at the heart of everything we do. To care for the Children admitted to Leicester Children&#39;s Hospital during the COVID pandemic and over our busy period of winter has resulted in the opportunity to offer short-term contracts. We are committed to continue to provide opportunities to develop the skills of the staff that are successful in gaining a short-term contract with us.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;We have positions on both of our Children&#39;s Surgical Wards. These areas provide specialist surgical care to Children from Leicestershire and further afield. Successful applicants will have chance to work along-side our award winning Pain team, gain experience from the Specialist Nurses who support our wards and be part of wards that are motivated and enthusiastic in the care they give their Children.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;Applicants can be experienced or newly qualified Children’s Nurses. &lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Clare Suart, Matron&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Email address: clare.suart@uhl-tr.nhs.uk,     07790825554&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Additional contact information:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Becky Morley, Ward sister on Ward 10, 0116 2585362&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;or&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Warren Sims, Ward manager on Ward 19, 0116 2585244&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
